data.value: SELECT A.START_DATE , A.END_DATE , A.YOYANG_GIHO , A.YOYANG_NAME , A.YOYANG_NAME2 , A.ZIP_CODE1 , A.ZIP_CODE2 , A.ZIP_CODE , A.ADDRESS , A.ADDRESS1 , A.TEL , A.TEL1 , A.FAX , A.TOT_BED , A.HOMEPAGE , A.EMAIL , A.HOSP_JIN_GUBUN , A.DODOBUHYEUN_NO , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('DODOBUHYEUN_NO', A.DODOBUHYEUN_NO) , A.JAEDAN_NAME , A.SIMPLE_YOYANG_NAME , A.BANK_NAME , A.BANK_JIJUM , A.BANK_NO , A.BANK_ACC_NAME , A.PRESIDENT_NAME , A.ORCA_GIGWAN_CODE FROM BAS0001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code ORDER BY TO_CHAR(A.START_DATE, 'YYYYMMDD') || A.YOYANG_GIHO DESC
